                        <condition key="other">
                           <p>Good. The manuscript bears traces of extensive use. </p>
                           <p>The original sewing is broken. Two nylon strings are led through the gut margin of all folios. The outer margin of fol. <locus target="#59"/>has been trimmed. The text and a drawing (of a human figure?) on fol. <locus target="#59va"/>are abraded.</p>
                           
