                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="mixed" xml:id="d3">
                        <p>- Fol. <locus target="#1r"/>: crude polychrome ornamental band (anthropomorphic motif: human face).</p>
                        <p>- Fol. <locus target="#3r #40r"/>: recent illustrations unrelated to the main tex, painted over the text.</p>
                        
